---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout lang="en" routeKey="home" title="Page not found | PUPA Center" description="The page you are looking for does not exist. Find your way back to PUPA Center.">
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>Page not found · Halaman tidak ditemukan · 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다</h1>
      <p class="lede">The page you are looking for does not exist or has moved. · Halaman yang Anda cari tidak ada atau telah dipindahkan. · 찾으시는 페이지가 존재하지 않거나 이동되었습니다.</p>
      <div class="nf-ctas">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Go to homepage</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/id/">Ke beranda (ID)</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/ko/">홈으로 (KO)</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
<style>
.page-head{background:var(--cream);padding:96px 0 120px;border-bottom:1px solid #EFE4D2}
.lede{font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:18px 0 30px}
.nf-ctas{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}
</style>
